net.sf.mmm.util.exception.api

Class ExceptionTruncation

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.exception.api.ExceptionTruncation

  • public class ExceptionTruncation
extends Object
    This class configures the (potential) truncation of an exception. A truncation includes the following aspects:
    • remove cause
    • remove stacktrace
    • remove suppressed exceptions
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
